
First we list the potential users of DICOMUX

 -> Doctor
 -> Patient
 -> Scientists
 -> Medicans
 -> 

This Document shows the different user workflows in the area of medical Data/ Information.

It can be that the User is not a computer/ software spezialist. 
Because of that the user want to act instinctively with any computer.


1)
A doctor can get differnent measurements about a patient from one or more sources.
This measurements are stored in one Dicom File. The doctor wants to see the measurements to make a diagnose.
To make a good diagnose the doctor needs a overview and a detailed view of all measurements.

2)
A user can have a patient historie. The user wants to compare different measurements. 
If the measurements from the patient got better or worst the user wants to see that.

3)
If a user has a collection of measurements in one single file the user may want to filter this collection 
and save only a part of this collection in a new file.
     